- import_tasks: x.yml 
  with_items: [1,2,3] 
 
This willi import x.yml one time and every imported task will now run 
and loop over 1,2,3 
 
- include_tasks: x.yml 
  with_items: [1,2,3] 
 
This will include x.yml 3 times and set the 'item' variable to 1, 2 
and 3 respectively 
